extraordinaire.

00:44.210 --> 00:48.506
He works very hard, so on Sundays,
just like Yahweh, he likes to kick back.

00:48.590 --> 00:50.717
[chuckling] <i>He invites all kinds of folks!</i>

00:50.800 --> 00:54.387
<i>Writers, directors, agents, producers,</i>
<i>you name it!</i>

00:54.471 --> 00:56.765
<i>Movie stars, like Tallulah Bankhead...</i>

00:56.848 --> 00:59.642
