I'm as pure as the driven slush.

01:03.438 --> 01:05.440
[all laughing]

01:05.523 --> 01:09.110
[Ernie] <i>...Vivien Leigh, and regular Joes</i>
<i>like yours truly.</i>

01:09.194 --> 01:10.945
<i>It's a bit of a caste system.</i>

01:11.029 --> 01:12.572
<i>The stars get French wine,</i>

01:12.655 --> 01:15.742
<i>the guys like us,</i>
<i>we get the swill from California.</i>

01:16.201 --> 01:17.035
