to have a mentor like you.

16:25.317 --> 16:26.402
It's what I do.

16:26.902 --> 16:28.612
[chuckles] Yeah.

16:31.573 --> 16:33.117
But you need more than me.

16:35.744 --> 16:37.538
Henry Willson just telephoned me.

16:38.122 --> 16:39.915
He's good friends with Dick Samuels.

16:39.999 --> 16:42.710
