up for this role...

16:43.544 --> 16:44.628
Rock Hudson.

16:44.712 --> 16:47.297
If you don't get somebody like Henry
in your corner,

16:47.381 --> 16:48.757
you're not going to stand a chance.

16:53.345 --> 16:57.725
