17:18.037 --> 17:19.788
-[door closes]
-[exhales] Oh, God.

17:22.207 --> 17:23.375
Have you seen this?

17:24.418 --> 17:28.297
Howard Hughes
got his <i>Spruce Goose</i> off the ground.

17:29.214 --> 17:31.175
That guy's a fuckin' lunatic.

17:32.009 --> 17:34.887
-Where have you been?
-You know, reading scripts.

17:36.430 --> 17:38.640
I've decided to gather
some of the ladies of Hollywood

17:38.724 --> 17:40.559
to cheer up Eleanor Roosevelt.

17:40.642 --> 17:43.479
She still hasn't gotten over
the whole Lucy Rutherford thing,

17:43.562 --> 17:46.398
and I hear lately
she has a real hangdog look about her.

17:46.482 --> 17:47.566
It's called her face.

17:48.275 --> 17:49.151
Charming.

17:50.069 --> 17:51.653
