You know why?

19:27.082 --> 19:30.586
Because then you will see
with your own two eyes

19:30.669 --> 19:33.255
that you do not have what it takes,
sweetheart.

19:33.338 --> 19:36.049
Ace Amberg!
If you so much as consider it--

19:36.133 --> 19:37.467
Hey! Hey!

19:38.218 --> 19:40.345
