I'm ready to sign.

20:22.346 --> 20:23.555
Telegram for Mrs. Cooper.

20:23.805 --> 20:25.557
Oh, how lovely.

20:28.560 --> 20:29.728
Whatever can it be?

20:31.271 --> 20:32.272
[gasps]

20:32.439 --> 20:34.191
Oh, this telegram says that...

20:34.274 --> 20:35.901
Andrew is alive.

20:36.860 --> 20:38.695
Oh, they've found him alive!

20:39.112 --> 20:41.198
[lawyer] Mrs. Cooper! Mrs. Cooper!

20:41.657 --> 20:43.575
