Let me go get some smellin' salts!

20:48.413 --> 20:49.623
[whimpering]

20:49.706 --> 20:51.083
-Cut!
-[stage bell rings]

20:51.166 --> 20:53.835
Oh, I think she was right.
That line is so much better.

20:53.919 --> 20:55.420
