20:55.504 --> 21:00.133
You say the lines as scripted
or you can get your ass off this set!

21:00.217 --> 21:01.677
-[sighs]
-Do you hear me?

21:01.760 --> 21:02.594
Yes, sir.

21:02.678 --> 21:04.638
You do it again, and you're fired.

21:05.555 --> 21:07.599
That's a wrap. I'm going home.

21:07.683 --> 21:09.810
[crew man] Okay, folks. That's our day.

21:11.853 --> 21:13.063
[door opens]

21:13.146 --> 21:14.648
