22:08.702 --> 22:11.788
it's a parable about
how Hollywood treats an outsider.

22:11.872 --> 22:15.459
Oh, that's good. That's really good.
Oh, that's good. Oh!

22:16.710 --> 22:18.211
I'm the best actress at Ace Pictures.

22:18.545 --> 22:20.922
-You <i>are</i> the best, baby.
-You know it, and the studio knows it.

22:21.006 --> 22:22.215
You're the fucking best, baby.

22:22.299 --> 22:25.218
-So you'll think about it?
-I'll think about it. It's a great idea.

22:26.511 --> 22:27.471
No, really.

22:28.722 --> 22:31.683
