opposite one another,

23:20.899 --> 23:24.069
and we'll both have a leg up
on our competition.

23:24.820 --> 23:25.695
You free Sunday?

23:26.405 --> 23:29.282
Oh, Claire... I would love to.

23:30.534 --> 23:32.327
