23:38.333 --> 23:39.209
Yeah.

23:39.292 --> 23:40.335
Wow, that was fast.

23:40.919 --> 23:42.003
Rain check, then.

23:42.504 --> 23:43.505
Oh...

23:44.423 --> 23:45.424
Yeah.

23:48.176 --> 23:49.803
-[cigarette sizzles]
-Ah, fuck!

23:51.012 --> 23:56.643
