that I'm unaware of?

24:11.450 --> 24:12.367
Oh, yes.

24:12.742 --> 24:15.912
You're oblivious because you don't
have to lurk in the shadows.

24:15.996 --> 24:18.707
And I said, "George is still my director!"

24:18.790 --> 24:20.417
And for all the scenes, the real ones,

24:20.500 --> 24:22.502
the ones that really needed
my heart and soul,

24:22.586 --> 24:25.046
I came over here and I rehearsed them
with George by the pool.

24:25.130 --> 24:27.507
Jack, try to spend some time with Henry.

24:29.593 --> 24:31.094
Do <i>you</i> shop at the market?

24:32.304 --> 24:33.138
Never been.

24:33.221 --> 24:36.558
It is still his movie,
I don't care what anyone says.

24:36.641 --> 24:38.602
Thanks, Viv, that's sweet of you.

24:39.144 --> 24:41.730
Don't eat a bunch,
I'm gonna introduce you to Vivien.

24:41.813 --> 24:44.191
