24:49.821 --> 24:51.156
Nice to meet you, Jack.

24:51.740 --> 24:52.616
Noel Coward.

24:53.283 --> 24:54.326
Pleasure to meet you.

24:55.619 --> 24:57.204
Would you just look at Richard?

24:57.829 --> 24:59.498
He's the most perfect gentleman.

24:59.998 --> 25:01.791
Style, whole demeanor.

25:01.958 --> 25:04.002
Ellen, why don't you just fuck him?

25:04.753 --> 25:07.672
