25:10.967 --> 25:13.970
It's not my fault
he was run over by a streetcar.

25:14.054 --> 25:18.266
Vivien, I'd like to introduce you
to a client, this is Rock Hudson.

25:18.683 --> 25:19.684
-Pleasure.
-Hi.

25:21.228 --> 25:23.021
So I take it you're in <i>Gone with the Wind?</i>

25:24.022 --> 25:25.649
-Yes, yes...
-Are you fucking kidding?

25:25.732 --> 25:29.277
She's goddamn Scarlett O'Hara,
