25:53.927 --> 25:58.056
-"Not going to be a war..."
-You do not want to die in a single bed.

25:58.139 --> 26:01.851
People will talk and you know it.
Old maid.

26:01.935 --> 26:04.187
God, Avis, you can be a vile drunk.

26:05.188 --> 26:07.607
"As God is my witness,
