26:08.066 --> 26:09.317
Old maid.

26:09.401 --> 26:10.819
[door bell rings]

26:11.194 --> 26:12.571
[Ernie] Pretty swanky, huh?

26:13.113 --> 26:14.739
-You look great, kid.
-[Archie chuckles]

26:15.282 --> 26:16.783
It's gonna be a hell of a night.

26:17.951 --> 26:19.286
Mrs. Amberg.

26:20.745 --> 26:21.913
Avis, sweetheart.

26:21.997 --> 26:24.499
Ernie, baby. [giggling]

26:24.791 --> 26:25.834
[both moan]

26:26.001 --> 26:27.335
You're not leaving, are you?

26:27.419 --> 26:29.296
[Ellen] Yes, I'm going to drive her home.

26:29.379 --> 26:31.840
We had a little bit too much
