26:31.923 --> 26:34.301
-[Avis giggling]
-All sheets to the wind, I'm afraid.

26:34.384 --> 26:36.386
Good night, Ernie. See you soon?

26:37.053 --> 26:38.013
I'll see you real soon.

26:38.096 --> 26:40.765
Wish I could stay to see those USC boys.

26:41.141 --> 26:43.435
-[Ernie chuckling]
-Oh! Ah! [giggles]

26:43.643 --> 26:44.477
[Ellen] Come on.

26:44.936 --> 26:46.688
