26:57.407 --> 27:00.160
-Mm.
-She's always had a soft spot for you.

27:00.243 --> 27:01.328
I'll go say hello.

27:03.204 --> 27:04.289
Hi, I'm George.

27:04.831 --> 27:05.749
Welcome.

27:09.002 --> 27:10.879
[indistinct chatter]

27:18.345 --> 27:19.179
Jack.

27:20.138 --> 27:21.973
