All right?

27:38.031 --> 27:39.866
[man] It's not warm, it's freezing!

27:40.241 --> 27:41.618
[all cheering]

27:46.164 --> 27:47.165
Sidecar, please.

27:49.751 --> 27:50.585
Hi.

27:51.503 --> 27:53.713
[stutters] You're directing <i>Peg,</i> right?

27:54.714 --> 27:57.342
