from the gas station,

29:00.113 --> 29:01.573
if you get what I'm saying.

29:03.533 --> 29:06.494
You gotta do what you gotta do
to follow your dreams.

29:07.120 --> 29:08.163
I admire that.

29:09.539 --> 29:10.749
